commitResults.messageBody:
* Wire score serialization into JsonSerializableAddressBook:
  add subjectScores field, accept in @JsonCreator, populate on save,
  and convert DTOs to model in toModelType().
* Add JsonAdaptedScoreEntry for storing (personName, score) pairs.
* Enable subject enrollment during load by exposing enrollPerson() on Subject.
* Allow storage layer to set scores during load (make ScoreDict.setScore() and removePerson() public).
* Add temporary defaults in Model for compatibility with existing test stubs.
